Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.58,0:00:27.54,Dialogue-italic,,0000,0000,0000,derp,Back then, mom was still alive, and dad was kind. Back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.77,0:00:30.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,derp,Say, Kyou-chan...
