Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.96,0:00:38.40,Dialogue-italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, I made a promise to mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.96,0:00:41.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A very important promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.52,0:00:44.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan! Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.93,0:00:46.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:50.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.00,0:00:54.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if your fever is gone yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.62,0:00:58.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.73,0:01:01.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My temperature is the same as yours, so that means it's gone!{FORESHADOWING}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.80,0:01:04.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go deliver the newspapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.46,0:01:05.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.33,0:01:08.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.76,0:01:11.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, don't go out there.{you can't}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.92,0:01:13.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.59,0:01:18.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you went on your newspaper run during rainy days, your cold got even worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.62,0:01:22.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! It's all about mind over matter!{病は気から 【やまいはきから】 (exp) sickness and health start with the mind}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.44,0:01:25.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, you should really stay in bed!{blarg}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.28,0:01:40.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother went to heaven the year she gave birth to Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.51,0:01:43.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Our father disappeared after accumulating gambling debts.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.34,0:01:47.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, we were abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.65,0:01:52.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a 40-year-old, one-room, dilapidated apartment with no bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.84,0:01:55.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.19,0:01:57.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, when spring comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.13,0:03:54.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, the rice porridge is done!{粥 【かゆ】 (n) thin rice porridge; watery cooked rice; rice gruel;}
