Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.52,0:13:18.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'd love to hear Ichinokura-san's song.{idk anymore. bleh}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.82,0:13:21.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, I feel like it'd help me get better.{fuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuu}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.81,0:13:27.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll sing because you said so, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:35.83,Dialogue-italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan is late, huh?{on another note, WHY DOESN'T THIS GUY LEARN A NEW FUCKING SONG OH WELL AT LEAST THAT SAVES ME THE AGONY OF FIXING THE HORRIBLY TRANSLATED LYRICS OF AN ALL NEW MASTERPIECE}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:03.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dandelions...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:06.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:17.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,derp,These are Mom's favorite flowers!{hm, rather than sepia, maybe I should add some kind of bloom or something}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.16,0:14:31.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,derp,I'll take some to Mom in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.82,0:14:35.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,derp,Mom always smiles when she sees dandelions!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.01,0:14:39.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,derp,That's why, if I bring them to her, she'll get better again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.32,0:14:47.52,Dialogue-italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, I would gather flowers day after day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.51,0:14:54.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,derp,Mom! Mom! I brought you some more flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.24,0:15:12.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.46,0:15:16.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There was nothing I could do.{probably could be better linked to the current situation}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.11,0:15:18.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.70,0:15:23.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,derp,Kyou, you brought me some dandelions again, didn't you?{DANDELIONS IN A VASE, YOU SEE FLOWERS IN THESE WEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEDS}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.13,0:15:26.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.73,0:15:30.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.18,0:15:32.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I promised, I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.31,0:15:34.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,derp,Thank you.{k so would it be weird to make her mom's speech all bloom-y >__>}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.10,0:15:39.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,derp,Looking at the dandelions you've brought me always helps me forget about my sickness.{FUCK. FUCK. FUCK.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:45.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:49.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom's smile... She looks so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.20,0:15:52.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,derp,Hey, mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.78,0:15:57.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,derp,Why do you smile whenever you see dandelions?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.04,0:16:00.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,derp,You see, it's because the dandelions look so happy and carefree to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.76,0:16:01.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,derp,They look happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.94,0:16:02.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,derp,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.88,0:16:06.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,derp,That's why they remind me of you, Kyou-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.06,0:16:07.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,derp,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.41,0:16:08.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,derp,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:13.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,derp,Just like the dandelions, you always seem to be smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:16.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,derp,That's why I smile whenever I see dandelions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.65,0:16:18.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,derp,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.33,0:16:25.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Mom wasn't smiling because she was looking at the dandelions...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.99,0:16:29.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She was looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.58,0:16:33.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She was smiling because she saw my smile.{"face" is a more accurate translation but I really like this phrasing better.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.03,0:16:35.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:39.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.72,0:16:40.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:43.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.92,0:16:58.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I never smiled for Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.18,0:17:00.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.86,0:17:03.02,Dialogue-italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.70,0:17:06.80,Dialogue-italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, don’t try to take anybody else’s place.{lifted right out of episode 4, 17:54}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.80,0:17:07.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Asu.{I'm like 90% sure they just forgot to animate her mouth. I think that explains why it magically disappeared.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:14.74,Dialogue-italic,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re my older sister. Stay that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.67,0:17:19.33,Dialogue-italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I will. I'll be right here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:21.85,Dialogue-italic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.17,0:17:27.69,Dialogue-italic,,0000,0000,0000,,I... What the heck was I doing? I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.09,0:17:39.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Asu!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.94,0:17:41.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd forgotten!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.25,0:17:46.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing that only I can do for Asu. The most important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.71,0:17:48.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd forgotten!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.21,0:17:57.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Onee-chan is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:18:01.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope she hasn't tired herself out worrying about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:06.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to handle the hospital fees, too. Maybe I'm just being an annoyance to her.{for fuck's sake could these people be any more self-deprecating}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.80,0:18:24.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:35.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.98,0:18:42.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:44.41,Dialogue-italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.09,0:18:46.34,Dialogue-italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.97,0:18:53.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan's smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.63,0:18:56.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks just like a dandelion!{okay, I lost it. I just... }
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:02.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations on being discharged, Asu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.71,0:19:04.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.40,0:19:06.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure to take it easy for a while, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.01,0:19:06.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.69,0:19:08.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for all you've done.{WHY DO YOU NEED TO THANK THEM, YOU'RE FUCKING PAYING THEM FOR IT :V}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.11,0:19:15.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Onee-chan, there's a place I'd like to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.75,0:19:26.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't push yourself too much, okay?{tough it out like that anymore}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.47,0:19:26.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.41,0:19:31.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, at first, your cold was far worse than mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.05,0:19:35.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so worried about you that I forgot to take care of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.57,0:19:36.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.71,0:19:40.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.21,0:19:40.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.98,0:19:44.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.43,0:19:48.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here, Mom asked me to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:53.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a long time ago, but this is where I heard it.{um wait...}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.94,0:19:57.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,derp,I'm your big sister! Do you understand me?{JESUS CHRIST HOW MANY TIMES WILL THEY REPEAT THIS}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:00.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.85,0:20:03.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Along with Mom's voice.{these are fragments. DO I LOOK LIKE I GIVE A FUCK}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:06.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,derp,I ask you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.91,0:20:08.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,derp,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.06,0:20:10.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,derp,Your big sister...{idk this is probably supposed to be broken english anyway but fuck that shitniggersidon'tgiveafucksofuckthatshityoufuckingfaggots}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.78,0:20:12.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Your big sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.17,0:20:14.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please protect her", she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.24,0:20:19.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Asu, Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.70,0:20:24.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't remember this{her} at all, but I get the feeling that that was what I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:27.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I've promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.48,0:20:30.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I'll protect her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.51,0:20:32.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I will protect Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.66,0:20:43.86,Dialogue-italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.45,0:20:47.79,Dialogue-italic,,0000,0000,0000,,We're keeping our promises.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.82,0:20:54.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a 40-year-old, one-room, dilapidated apartment with no bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.28,0:20:57.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.53,0:21:00.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, when spring comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.88,0:21:06.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Onee-chan, look, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.70,0:21:08.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, they're in full bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.93,0:21:17.23,Dialogue-italic,,0000,0000,0000,,We're very happy together!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.81,0:21:22.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, this is bad! Really bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.05,0:21:24.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The sakura-viewing has come inside!{heh heh heh... c wat i did thar?}
